:09:26.000Z","msg":"Shawshank 自我救贖<br />\nStand by me 友誼長存<br />\n放牛班的春天 因材施教<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e502b8eb703f195421713d3ff28fd11368308996","tid":517933,"uid":155156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232b0142f1f9d4c767b4f9587b52bf2c2d079c5e","tid":517933,"uid":57851,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T00:21:23.000Z","msg":"Mr. Nobody"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"一直想番睇<br />\n睇一次真係未明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a51d7e52fa93cde31131ce6baf72f4fa1b7f88b","tid":517933,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f14d5756ad44da51503707bc51c5e834eee75744","tid":517933,"uid":137037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8176bc77268a9f97844d5c7e04d521bc7f4a215","tid":517933,"uid":112436,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"124cc57c293d87eb7c0df18b9d8fc1f356a68581","tid":517933,"uid":67237,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"真係會有人覺得呢套悶咩<br />\n事後再聽人講返愛迪生就覺得呢套更有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"同我一齊睇嘅兩個朋友都訓著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T17:40:36.000Z","msg":"估唔到有同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:11:41.000Z","msg":"x 3    果陣我超沉迷打機 <br />\n成日會租vcd 番屋企睇<br />\n只有極少數戲可以吸引到我睇哂<br />\n坐定定睇 唔走去打機<br />\n一年數埋未必有10套<br />\n<br />\n呢套係其中之一<br />\n睇完之後 第二日即刻翻睇<br />\n到而家 應該翻睇左多過十次<br />\n<br />\n而家諗起 , 最大體會係<br />\n原來做野動機未必一定只求名利 乜尻都唔理<br />\n純粹追求卓越, 追求成就感<br />\n都可以係一種合理又有型既人生態度<br />\n<br />\n劇情大橋唔係話特別好勁<br />\n但敘事手法 , 場景 對白 演技<br />\n都係好易令人投入<br />\n乜野都交待得岩岩好<br />\n睇戲睇我投入最緊要   <br />\n<br />\n另我個人心得係nolan 戲其中一個Theme成日Repeat <br />\n就係 主角係戲既最大任務係為左同仔女重聚<br />\nthe prestige 係第一套開始呢個theme<br />\n<br />\n<br />